# -*- conf -*-
OASISFormat:  0.4
OCamlVersion: >= 4.03.0
Name:         brotli
Version:      1.2.0
Maintainers:  Edgar Aroutiounian
Homepage:     http://hyegar.com
Synopsis:     Bindings to Google's Brotli compresion algorithm
Authors:      Edgar Aroutiounian <edgar.factorial@gmail.com>
License:      BSD-3-clause
Plugins:      META (0.4), DevFiles (0.4)
AlphaFeatures: ocamlbuild_more_args

Description:
  OCaml Bindings to brotli, Google's new compression algorithm

  Uses Bigarrays for memory efficiency and ready for Lwt concurrency
  Source: https://github.com/google/brotli/
  RFC: http://www.ietf.org/id/draft-alakuijala-brotli

Library brotli
  Path: src
  BuildTools:ocamlbuild
  install: true
  CClib:
    -L/usr/local/lib -lbrotlidec -lbrotlienc -lc++
  CCOpt:
    -Wextra -fno-omit-frame-pointer
    -fsanitize=undefined-trap -fsanitize-undefined-trap-on-error
    -O2 -fsanitize=address -fno-optimize-sibling-calls
    -g -Wall -std=c++14 -x c++ -I/usr/local/include 
  NativeOpt:
    -cc clang++ -g -w +a-4-40..42-44-45-48
    -cclib -fsanitize=address -ccopt -fsanitize=address
  ByteOpt:
    -cc clang++ -g -w +a-4-40..42-44-45-48
    -cclib -fsanitize=address -ccopt -fsanitize=address
  Modules: Brotli
  BuildDepends: bigarray
  CSources: brotli_stubs.c

Executable stress_test
  Path: example
  BuildTools:ocamlbuild
  install: false
  MainIs: e.ml
  CompiledObject: native
  NativeOpt: -g -w +a-4-40..42-44-45-48
  ByteOpt: -g -w +a-4-40..42-44-45-48
  BuildDepends: brotli


Document api
  Title: API reference for brotli
  Type: ocamlbuild (0.4)
  Authors: Edgar Aroutiounian
  BuildTools: ocamldoc, ocamlbuild
  Format: HTML
  Index: index.html
  XOCamlbuildPath: .
  XOCamlbuildLibraries: brotli
